title: Hey, I'm Armel
bio:
I'm a final-year PhD student at **Inria Paris** in the [ALMAnaCH](https://almanach.inria.fr/index-en.html) team, working under the supervision of [Rachel Bawden](https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=G3DS5GAAAAAJ&hl=fr) and [Beno√Æt Sagot](https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=HXUT9ZkAAAAJ&hl=fr) on **Machine Translation**. My research focuses on improving the ability of LLMs to translate into low-resource languages.

I hold an Engineer's degree from Ecole Polytechnique and a M.S. degree from ENS Paris-Saclay (MVA).

When not doing research, I sleep.
